original_title: Westlife: Live in Stockholm The Turnaround Tour
overview: Turnaround Tour covered the UK and Europe in 2004, the tour was also supposed to appear in China, Korea, Malaysia, Thailand, Philippines and Singapore however it was cancelled. Member Bryan McFadden left the group just 3 weeks before the first date of this tour in Belfast.
title: Westlife: Live in Stockholm The Turnaround Tour
